'''Albay''' <b title="Pronunciation: al&middot;BAI, /{l&quot;baI/" style="position:relative;top:-0.3em;font-size:0.75em;color:#666;">P</b> metung yang [[Ding Lalawigan ning Filipinas|lalawigan]] ning [[Filipinas]] a atiu king [[Ding Labuad king Filipinas|Labuad]][[Labuad Bicol|Bicol]] king  [[Luzon]]. Ing kayang balen tungku ya pin ing [[Syudad Legazpi]] at makasepu ya keng [[Camarines Sur]] king pangulu at [[Sorsogon]] king mauli. Makanyan mu rin king pangulung aslagan ya pin ing [[Lagonoy Gulf]] papuntang [[Dayat Malat ning Filipinas]], at king maulingalbugan ya pin ing [[Burias Pass]].

